rp teeth may fall out when worn away or after an impact, but they regrow within a few days."}, {"version": "moon", "text": "It skulks in caves, and when prey or an enemy passes by, it leaps out and chomps them. The force of its attack sometimes chips its teeth."}, {"version": "omega-ruby", "text": "It nests in horizontal holes warmed by geothermal heat. Foes who get too close can expect to be pounced on and bitten."}, {"version": "pearl", "text": "It once lived in the tropics. To avoid the cold, it lives in caves warmed by geothermal heat."}, {"version": "platinum", "text": "It attacks using its huge mouth. While its attacks are powerful, it hurts itself out of clumsiness, too."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "Gible attacks anything that moves, and it drags whatever it catches into the crevice that is its lair. Despite the big mouth, Gible\u2019s stomach is small."}, {"version": "soulsilver", "text": "It nests in horizontal holes warmed by geothermal heat. Foes who get too close can expect to be pounced on and bitten."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "It lives in caves warmed by geothermal heat. Even so, when the weather gets cold, it will huddle close with others of its kind."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "Gible prefers to stay in narrow holes in the sides of caves heated by geothermal energy. This way, Gible can stay warm even during a blizzard."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "Its original home is an area much hotter than Alola. If you\u2019re planning to live with one, your heating bill will soar."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "It reacts to anything that moves\u2014flies right at it and bites it. Sometimes it injures itself, but it doesn\u2019t care too much."}, {"version": "white", "text": "It attacks using its huge mouth. While its attacks are powerful, it hurts itself out of clumsiness, too."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "It attacks using its huge mouth. While its attacks are powerful, it hurts itself out of clumsiness, too."}, {"version": "x",